values: Disappointed that Nintendo is shutting down club Nintendo seeing as they have my email and no notification was sent to it. Just happened to buy a new game and was updating 3ds and went to site and logged in. It was nice of them to give options of games to download before 6/30/2015 They could have just shutdown with a sorry we are moving on. But the selection is weighted heavily towards wiiU. For the amount of points I had chose the best they offered. Check out The Legend of Zelda: Link's Awakening via Club Nintendo
Went and found a layout that I liked. I got it from <lj user="fruitstyle">
